high_descs: walk to face the counter with the coffee maker
open the cabinet on the left below the coffee maker, pick up the kettle, close the door
walk to the right to face the sink
put the kettle in the sink, wash, pick up the kettle from the sink
walk left to face the counter top with the coffee maker
put the kettle on the counter in front of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: put a washed kettle in front of a coffee maker

high_descs: Turn right, move to the sink, turn left, move to the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the kettle from in the lower left cabinet under the coffee machine.
Turn around, bring the kettle to the sink on the left.
Wash the kettle in the sink with water.
Turn left, bring the kettle to the coffee machine.
Put the kettle on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned kettle on the counter in front of the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right, go to sink, turn left, go to counter with coffee maker on it.
Open lower cabinet, remove kettle from cabinet, close cabinet.
Turn around, proceed to sink on left.  Turn left to face sink.
Put kettle in sink, fill with water, empty water, pick up kettle from sink.
Put kettle on counter in front of coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Get kettle out of cabinet, wash kettle, put kettle on counter.
